name: Intro To Data Science: Online Workshop
description: JGet dressed to impress, sip and Mingle. This will be our very first event. There will be light refreshments and some background music in a space you can take photos in your stylishEnsemble while you feast your eyes on everyone's personal taste.

name: Streets of Bushwick
description: 'Streets of Bushwick' is this month's RLP Photographer's Meetup. It is a freestyle street photography event so shoot what moves you. There are many subjects to shoot in this ever-changing Brooklyn neighborhood. It is still Autumn in New York City. Let's take in the beauty of Fall while on the streets of Bushwick.

name: How to Become a Data Professional with No Experience
description: Did you know data science and data analytics are among the fastest-growing career paths globally? Whether you have previous knowledge or little to no experience, this workshop will offer actionable tips for how you can begin your tech career in less than one year. Register today to save your spot.

name: Social & Networking
description: Join us for our third Data & Drinks meet-up in NYC! This event will be an informal event to discuss data and network. We'd love for anyone to join, and we will have a small sign on the table to identify the group.
